high_descs: turn right to face the fridge
grab a potato off of the top shelves of the fridge
move to the right a bit and face the microwave there
place the potato inside of the microwave, close the door, let it cook for a bit, then open the door and take it back out, and close the door
move to the left a bit and face the microwave again
place the potato down on top of the counter the microwave is on
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved potato down on top of the kitchen counter

high_descs: Take out the potato from the refrigerator on the same shelf as the bowl, then close the refrigerator.
Turn right and walk to the microwave on the small side table to the right of the refrigerator.
Heat the potato in the microwave for a few seconds, then take it out and close the microwave.
Turn left and walk forward slightly, then turn right towards the side table again.
Put the potato on the table, to the left of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot potato on a small side table.

high_descs: Turn right to face the fridge then look up.
Open the fridge and grab the potato that's on the shelf under the egg then close the door.
Take a step to your right to face the microwave.
Cook the potato in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Take a tiny step to your left.
Put the potato under the green cup on the right edge of the microwave's counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato on the counter.
